# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Meekatharra

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 102 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Meekatharra, of which three are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following three state registered places within the Shire of Meekatharra:
